      • observePatterns

        public reactor.core.publisher.Flux<PatternMessage<K,V>> observePatterns()
        从接口复制的说明: RedisPubSubReactiveCommands
        Flux for messages (pmessage) received though pattern subscriptions. The connection needs to be subscribed to one or more patterns using RedisPubSubReactiveCommands.psubscribe(Object[]).

        Warning! This method uses FluxSink.OverflowStrategy.BUFFER This does unbounded buffering and may lead to OutOfMemoryError. Use RedisPubSubReactiveCommands.observePatterns(FluxSink.OverflowStrategy) to specify a different strategy.

        指定者:
        observePatterns 在接口中 RedisPubSubReactiveCommands<K,V>
        返回:
        hot Flux for subscriptions to pmessage's.
